body:
So I got the notification message saying I had been promoted honor levels but on inspection of my profile my honor level was unchanged.

I sent through a ticket to support and this is the response I received; 

&gt; Hey there,
&gt; 
&gt; That does seem to be the case, we are looking at investigating what&#039;s causing this problem, and when we find the fix we will change your honor to the appropriate level. There might be a wait, but we will get to it asap.

The whole Honor System update doesn&#039;t seem very well thought out or even tested at all before implementation.
